me, my door's always open.

08:16.116 --> 08:17.611
It's a drive, bringing
here back here, Raymond.

08:17.635 --> 08:18.853
Hey, look, that's enough.

08:18.877 --> 08:19.706
Just sit still.

08:23.364 --> 08:25.170
Thanks, Marty.
Yeah, sure.

08:25.194 --> 08:27.437
I gotta get going.
Okay.

08:34.652 --> 08:36.722
Ew, gross, Mommy.

08:45.973 --> 08:47.837
Hey, Lawrence, come on.

08:49.598 --> 08:50.460
