lives trying to be original.

08:58.399 --> 09:00.401
You, you're lucky
enough to be born one.

09:04.820 --> 09:07.167
Just get yourself some chips.

09:16.314 --> 09:18.109
Just don't look
at him, baby girl.

09:35.885 --> 09:37.611
Mommy!
Oh, my God.

10:16.063 --> 10:18.973
Where are we?

