11:57.855 --> 11:58.683
Ray.

12:02.652 --> 12:03.446
Hey.

12:05.863 --> 12:06.656
Oh.

12:09.763 --> 12:10.799
I'm so sorry.

12:11.972 --> 12:14.813
I don't understand,
what the fuck happened?

12:14.837 --> 12:16.563
Truck just came out of nowhere.

12:20.049 --> 12:21.395
Just the middle of the day.

12:23.397 --> 12:24.295
A regular day.

12:28.057 --> 12:29.610
I got me the first flight back.

12:32.061 --> 12:32.924
Oh, my God.

12:35.962 --> 12:37.249
Officer Marrow.

12:42.831 --> 12:43.659
Hey.

12:45.730 --> 12:47.501
Hi, Lawrence.

12:47.525 --> 12:49.561
That's right, I'm
Officer Marrow.

12:51.356 --> 12:52.806
This is your Aunt Caroline.

12:55.119 --> 12:56.579
Say hi.

12:56.603 --> 12:57.397
You're nice.

13:07.752 --> 13:09.374
Nice to finally meet you.

13:14.586 --> 13:16.796
Ooh, he's precocious.

13:19.453 --> 13:20.351
I just...

13:25.252 --> 13:27.127
I don't know what
the fuck I'm doin'.

13:27.151 --> 13:29.336
You know what, you're here.

13:29.360 --> 13:30.958
