13:40.716 --> 13:41.544
Okay.

13:44.513 --> 13:47.067
Well, I'll come by first
thing in the morning.

13:50.001 --> 13:51.220
You're here now, right?

13:51.244 --> 13:53.108
You better get used
to seeing my face.

13:54.316 --> 13:57.053
