or with Amanda and Burg?

13:57.077 --> 13:59.193
No, we're gonna stay here.

13:59.217 --> 14:00.046
Alright.

14:01.150 --> 14:02.541
Okay.

14:02.565 --> 14:03.359
Alright, then.

14:07.881 --> 14:08.709
Alright.

14:27.797 --> 14:29.316
