put Mommy in the ground?

14:40.431 --> 14:41.915
That's enough now, Lawrence.

14:43.468 --> 14:44.687
Time to go to sleep.

14:44.711 --> 14:45.539
You're tired.

14:46.989 --> 14:49.347
No, I'm not.
Yes, you are.

14:49.371 --> 14:51.891
Now I'm gonna be sleeping
right here next to you.

14:53.409 --> 14:54.238
Go to sleep.

15:22.093 --> 15:24.589
Have I ever let you down?

15:27.374 --> 15:28.444
If we do this,

15:30.136 --> 15:31.102
you gotta deliver,

15:32.069 --> 15:33.104
'cause if you don't,

15:34.243 --> 15:35.762
Denver's gonna wipe
us off the map.

15:40.422 --> 15:42.676
Hello, Shelly.

15:42.700 --> 15:44.678
Two well and a cup.

15:44.702 --> 15:45.530
Mm-hmm.

15:52.089 --> 15:53.193
Fuck Colorado.

15:54.608 --> 15:56.517
We make one call, first truck's
on the road in five minutes.

15:56.541 --> 15:58.336
Don't make me the
bad guy, Bernie.

15:59.199 --> 16:00.614
And that's a yes?

16:02.616 --> 16:03.686
Yeah.

16:29.885 --> 16:31.438
Who's your friend?

16:33.199 --> 16:34.959
Oh, we met on social media.

16:45.073 --> 16:46.395
Can I help you with
something, Bernie?

16:46.419 --> 16:48.007
I heard Ray's back in town.

16:51.355 --> 16:52.183
That's right.

16:54.116 --> 16:55.645
And I heard Maise Connely

16:55.669 --> 16:58.017
met her maker in the
form of an F-150.

17:03.574 --> 17:04.689
I figured somebody who knows

17:04.713 --> 17:06.346
how hard it is to lose somebody

17:06.369 --> 17:08.199
would be a little
bit more empathetic.

17:11.892 --> 17:13.515
You don't talk about her.

18:15.439 --> 18:17.072
How you doin', bud?

18:21.065 --> 18:21.893
Lawrence?

18:22.860 --> 18:24.355
I look pretty, Daddy.

18:24.379 --> 18:26.253
Jesus Christ,
what are you doing?

18:26.277 --> 18:27.554
You don't do that.

18:29.038 --> 18:30.947
Here.

18:30.971 --> 18:32.870
Why am I a boy this time, Daddy?

18:34.078 --> 18:35.942
Because your mom and
I asked for you, bud.

18:43.363 --> 18:45.538
I don't wanna yell at you.

18:46.677 --> 18:48.230
I'm here, okay?

18:51.199 --> 18:52.200
Do you here me, bud?

18:56.204 --> 18:57.274
Let's get you dressed.

18:59.103 --> 19:00.770
